name: KidsGottaEat
description:
KidsGottaEat is a Deflationary Reflection Charity Token on the Binance Smart Chain.
10% of every transaction goes to OperationLuncbox.org to feed kids in need. Also 10% of every transaction is redistributed back to KidsGottaEat Token holders, and 5% is burned.
At Operation Lunchbox Our mission is to make sure every student has sufficient groceries, so that hunger doesn't hurt their chances to succeed. #KidsGottaEat
